[Yet again, our heartfelt thanks to Ramon. During 2013 they had 14 outbreaks of anthrax. And remember it is mid-summer in Argentina at this time, early in the anthrax season.

A map of Argentina can be found at http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/americas/argentina_pol96.jpg, and a map of Buenos Aires province can be found at https://maps.google.com/maps?q=map+buenos+aires+province. Mar Chiquita is north-northeast of Mar del Plata. - Mod.MHJ

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: http://healthmap.org/r/9Kbv.]
